                                                           Text="1. Click 'Start Server' above â€” this launches a local HTTP server + cloudflared tunnel&#x0a;2. Wait for the public URL to appear (may take a few seconds)&#x0a;3. Copy the URL with the ðŸ“‹ button&#x0a;4. In ChatGPT Desktop: Settings â†’ Apps â†’ Create app&#x0a;5. Enable 'Developer Mode' (required for MCP)&#x0a;6. Paste the URL as 'MCP Server URL' and save&#x0a;7. ChatGPT can now use all CodeMerger tools"
