                                                           Text="Tip: The tunnel URL changes every time you restart. Update the URL in ChatGPT Desktop settings after each restart. cloudflared is downloaded automatically on first use (~30MB)."
                                                           ToolTip="cloudflared is Cloudflare's tunnel client. It creates a secure tunnel from your local machine to Cloudflare's edge network, making your local server accessible via a public URL without port forwarding."/>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                        </Border>
                                    </StackPanel>
                                </Border>

                                <!-- â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• CONNECTION STATUS OVERVIEW â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• -->
